does that actually mean?

773
00:58:39,436 --> 00:58:42,022
It just means, Mum, don't
ask personal questions.

774
00:58:46,235 --> 00:58:47,736
Right, that's enough. Come on.

775
00:58:51,615 --> 00:58:53,742
